snippet.title: The Sims 4 Get to Work: Official Detective Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Explore crime scenes, interrogate suspects, and solve crimes with the Detective career in The Sims 4 Get to Work Expansion Pack.

Learn more: http://bit.ly/1FQLJw9

For the first time ever, you control your Sims at their workplace in The Sims 4 Get to Work, available April 2015.
